Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.01,0:27:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.88,0:27:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.29,0:27:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.75,0:28:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,メゾン・ド・章樫。　通称…　妖館。\N
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.61,0:28:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ここに来て\Nここの人たちと出会えて→\N
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.97,0:28:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,君と出会えて　僕は…。\N
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.84,0:29:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次回　「妖狐×僕ＳＳ」…。\N
